1.title: Lethal, Kamikazee, Beer - Oh My!

episode of.title: Log on & Eat with Eden Grinshpan (TV Series 2013– )

1.plot: Eden Grinshpan gets primal with Mac Lethal for some crown prime rib, connects with a popular "Bitch Beer" blogger in Austin, joins the online food show Kamikaze Kitchen, delivers a mystery ingredient to Seoul Sausage Company.

2.title: Eating Big Cat Trucker Style

episode of.title: Log on & Eat with Eden Grinshpan (TV Series 2013– )

2.plot: Eden Grinshpan heads to Texas to visit an online foodie called Big Cat Trucker, meets a popular online reviewer named Stephanie Perez for some takoyaki balls in New York City's Lower East Side and a spicy chicken aficionado.

3.title: Healthy Duck Fat Fries

episode of.title: Log on & Eat with Eden Grinshpan (TV Series 2013– )

3.plot: In LA, Eden Grinshpan gets down and dirty with new blogging sensations, "The Foodie Girls", and meets celebrity-turned-food blogger, Mariel Hemingway. Then, she heads to RI to meet an Internet star with over 100 million views.

4.title: Eat Like a Mermaid

episode of.title: Log on & Eat with Eden Grinshpan (TV Series 2013– )

4.plot: Eden Grinshpan heads to New England to dive into lessons from a blogger and fish monger on eating like a mermaid, meets a classy online duo who believe social media is an integral part of dining, and cooks with a top chef.

5.title: Foodimentary, My Dear Watson

episode of.title: Log on & Eat with Eden Grinshpan (TV Series 2013– )

5.plot: In Birmingham, Alabama, Eden Grinshpan immerses herself in an online foodie revolution with nearly a million followers. In LA, Eden meets celebrity food blogger, Haylie Duff, for a delicious burger. She heads to a Crawfish Festival.

6.title: Taking BBQ Nuclear

episode of.title: Log on & Eat with Eden Grinshpan (TV Series 2013– )

6.plot: Eden Grinshpan meets up with two New York pizza bloggers, the brain behind internet sensation Vegan Black Meta, chows down on barbecue nuclear by an online pit maker and dances with showgirl bloggers.

imdb.title: Log on & Eat with Eden Grinshpan
akas: Log on & Eat with Eden Grinshpan (United States)
plot: How do the biggest food fanatics express their love of food? They take it to the internet of course! Eden Grinshpan travels the country to meet food bloggers and social media stars, as they invite her to devour favorite dishes.
